setWrappingRecommender


void setWrappingRecommender(org.apache.mahout.cf.taste.recommender.Recommender r)
Recommender to be used when the evaluated recommender is not able to recommend some item for a user (i.e., it returns a NaN). It could be useful to ensure that all the recommenders are evaluated under the same conditions (every ranking has the same length).

Parameters:
r - recommender to use when the evaluated recommender fails to estimate some preference
